quote>有無咩性感衣著相po黎睇下</blockquote><br />\n咁我地作為主辦一方都覺得貼參賽者既性感相或者可愛相係屬於支持者拉票既權利黎<br />\n所以主辦黎講我地屆時只會提供簡單照片以示公允<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁撚認真</blockquote><br />\n咁我唔用認真既tone去講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁多場我好難條條女都幫佢地去貼圖拉票喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都有自己野做架，希望大家明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地想支持鍾意果位瘋狂貼圖助選係無問題既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece182fc74963dc62544dfba2a0572872d876a43","tid":499662,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecccf496ef661b266741a1aa13c99dbddf81c2c4","tid":499662,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:21:30.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9097eb08f953011b2bc1e591a1f85e2906e5e7b9","tid":499662,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:26:43.000Z","msg":"靚湯明整容都可做女神<br />\n不如DQ吧"},{"pid":"e8f3386503fc1f93d422ade4d9a15d5f54b93ab1","tid":499662,"uid":135265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim